stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> active: setupAgent
    active --> active: PRODUCE token
    active --> awaiting_tool: tool call parsed
    awaiting_tool --> active: tool result settled
    awaiting_tool --> active: nudge (settle reject)
    active --> idle: free_text_stop
    active --> idle: pressure_critical
    active --> idle: pressure_softcut
    active --> idle: max_turns
    idle --> recovering: policy.onRecovery = extract
    recovering --> idle: extraction complete
    idle --> [*]: branch pruned (ensure)
